145
00:07:24,252 --> 00:07:25,184
Don't worry,

146
00:07:25,695 --> 00:07:28,633
sooner or later the Charmed Ones will follow, and when they do,

147
00:07:29,568 --> 00:07:31,071
we will have them.

148
00:07:32,534 --> 00:07:34,242
What if they don't take the bait?

149
00:07:35,343 --> 00:07:36,654
What if they live no more?

150
00:07:36,846 --> 00:07:38,795
Well then we'll mess up a few kids,

151
00:07:39,324 --> 00:07:42,088
and that's fun all by itself, no?

152
00:07:45,032 --> 00:07:49,313
Time to find our next Alice.

153
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:53,776
<i>Signs of course can be good or bad.</i>

154
00:07:54,133 --> 00:07:55,559
<i>But they should never be ignored.</i>

155
00:07:55,559 --> 00:07:58,445
