157
00:08:02,178 --> 00:08:03,278
It's totally ragged.

158
00:08:03,635 --> 00:08:07,282
- I don't know. They probably think this is drugs or something.
- It's not drugs. No way.

159
00:08:07,343 --> 00:08:10,452
This is something way more scary. But they just don't care.

160
00:08:10,856 --> 00:08:12,133
Nobody cares! We're teenagers!

161
00:08:12,916 --> 00:08:15,112
No, that girl Alyson just turned 20.

162
00:08:15,774 --> 00:08:17,005
