175
00:09:13,082 --> 00:09:15,184
<i>Signs don't always mean what we think they do.</i>

176
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:17,222
<i>They can after all be confusing.</i>

177
00:09:17,747 --> 00:09:21,650
<i>Especially into this world where we're constantly bombarded by them.</i>

178
00:09:22,097 --> 00:09:25,103
<i>Still it's up to us to interpretate them the best way we know how.</i>

179
00:09:25,285 --> 00:09:26,812
<i>It's called survival.</i>

180
00:09:33,708 --> 00:09:34,771
